data.description: This fabulous 1 bedroom (corner) unit has incredible views day and night of the lake and the city.  We are a full amenity building with a pool, doorman, gym, laundry and even a food market!  Steps to the lake, Wrigley Field, shopping, nightlife, a golf course, the LSD entrance and tons of public transportation options.  The unit has hardwood floor a new bathroom, dishwasher and a breakfast bar.  One indoor parking space may be available for sale as well.
